# Drift guard for the vendored State API contract.
#
# This records the sha256 of state-api-contract.md as vendored from the
# platform repo (orun-cloud/specs/epics/saas-orun-platform/state-api-contract.md).
#
# The Go test TestVendoredContractChecksum (internal/remotestate/contract_vendor_test.go)
# fails if specs/orun-cloud/vendored/state-api-contract.md no longer matches this
# digest. When that happens, re-vendor from orun-cloud or renegotiate the contract
# (see README.md in this directory for the procedure).
#
# mcp-tool-manifest.json (the MCP tool-plane contract exported from
# orun-cloud/packages/mcp — saas-mcp-server MCP9) is guarded the same way by
# TestVendoredManifestChecksum (internal/platformmcp/parity_test.go), which
# also pins the byte-identical go:embed copy in internal/platformmcp/.
#
# Format: <sha256>  <file>
